  <summary date="2020-02-03T21:01:29Z" status="Reported to House">State Allowance for a Variety of Exchanges Act or the SAVE Act

This bill allows the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to support the establishment of state-based health insurance exchanges in those states that have not already elected to do so. A state that receives a grant must ensure that the resulting exchange is self-sustaining by 2024.</summary>
